Date: 1993-10-01

Title: Fusion algebra at a rational level and cohomology of nilpotent

subalgebras of sl_2Comments: 11 pages

Journal-ref: Lett.Math.Phys. 31 (1994) 315-326

We define and calculate the fusion algebra of WZW model at a rational levelby cohomological methods. As a byproduct we obtain a cohomologicalcharacterization of admissible representations of $\widehat{\gtsl}_{2}$.